public message and the law does not apply 
how can we exercize freedom of speech if people cant read our 
message he said 
mcdonald acknowledged that borough officials began to look into 
the billboard after someone complained anonymously to police 
the complainant said the antiabortion message is distasteful 
and offensive and the picture of the baby on the sign is 
