the area of a skirmish involving the vincennes the frigate elmer 
montgomery and several armed iranian speedboats 
initially the us navy report said two speedboats were sunk a 
third was damaged and the vincennes shot down an iranian f14 
fighter the plane later proved to be the iran air jet which was 
on a scheduled flight to dubai from a combined militarycivilian 
airport at bandar abbas 
the battle was the first direct encounter between us warships 
and iranian armed craft since april 18 when us attacks on two 
iranian oil platforms in reprisal for the mining of a navy frigate 
started a day of combat in which six iranian craft were sunk or 
disabled 
