<TEXT>
matilde nunez gripped the 
edge of her wooden chair and strained to watch the little girl as 
she grabbed her ruffled skirts and sashayed across the stage 
thats it bonita thats the way to do it wailed the proud 
aunt of 7yearold manuela nunez whose dancing stole the show at 
