companies valued at 320 million in cash and stock it was 
announced wednesday 
mtm producer of such popular and critically acclaimed series as 
hill street blues and st elsewhere will retain its name 
management and creative philosophy after the takeover by television 
south plc officials said here and in london 
miss moore and three mtm officers will emerge from the deal with 
a 20 percent share in the buyer known as tvs producer of the 
television movie mandela and other programs aired on britains 
two independent networks 
tvs which is selling an additional 20 percent stake to two 
french media companies to raise money for the buyout gets mtms 
library of old tv shows popular on both sides of the atlantic and 
becomes britains biggest independent tv production company 
