country last year but dropped that plan after the october stock 
market crash dampened investors enthusiasm for new issues 
the tvs deal arrived at after 10 months of negotiations blends 
each companys desire to expand in the others area tvs chief 
executive james gatward said in london 
though officials at both the london and california news 
conferences said they hoped the companies could jointly produce 
shows there arent any specific plans to do so immediately 
blumenthal said 
